rows.label: qev065102_MSG0001
rows.name: Tch! Here come the lesser organisms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065102_MSG0002
rows.name: You will kneel before the glory of our queen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065102_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Slenna where this queen is.

rows.label: qev065102_MSG0003
rows.name: You've come all this way without knowing anything?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065102_MSG0004
rows.name: Then you will die in ignorance. Fortun commands it![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065102_MSG0005
rows.name:
Fortun has issued a command in response to your
barbaric display.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065102_MSG0006
rows.name: You are to be put to death immediately.[ST:wait ]
